 |archivedate = 14 March 2007
 |df          = dmy-all
}}</ref> UN resolutions call on the United Kingdom and Spain, both EU members, to reach an agreement over the status of Gibraltar.<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://daccess-dds-ny.un.org/doc/RESOLUTION/GEN/NR0/218/33/IMG/NR021833.pdf?OpenElement
 |title       = Resolution 2070: Question of Gibraltar
